{"tid":1449754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:58:02.000Z","uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"24faff555e69e120cdc76ebe722a2d936b255b25","tid":1449754,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:41.000Z","msg":"812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcplDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=3bf805a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcplDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=e0c3e8eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>[/quote]"},{"pid":"8ea8eb82338ece6e163588216ff867851841bf05","tid":1449754,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"一連"},{"pid":"fc703ddfe4dfceb6d8f6c6739562a7b5e16fa7af","tid":1449754,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"二連"},{"pid":"29113ea7f0a3c70cb6f81e0cedd2ff5876577e6b","tid":1449754,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"三連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5691ba25bf54d9ed17308382466ebd130944ca0","tid":1449754,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:00.000Z","msg":"四連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011ebda976a45d3fb90c53100be50382881ce9bf","tid":1449754,"uid":108422,"like":0,"